name: Catch a Pearl in a Depth of the Sea_earrings
description:
These beauties are made of 2 elements, the wavy one joined to the square frame wrapping it with solid silver wire and inserting pearls, hooks are handmade solid silver.

	Size:
4 cm x 2 cm (with hooks they are 5.5 cm)

name: Sparkling Dew_earrings
description: I did them with pure glass briolettes, lucid white and soft pink, i put 2 crystals, rings are filled with 2 rows of small glass beads… Everything is carefully wrapped with NON TARNISH brass wire. Hooks are hammered. I just love that look! Length – 8 cm, with hook. It’s enough a little wind touch on them, and lucid briolettes start dancing and sparkling, like a dew on a leaf!... You have to see that, it’s soo beautiful…

name: Spring's Green_bracelet
description:
This amazing vernal bracelet will beautify every lady! It is made up of green like a sea aventurine chips, icy crystals and green crystals, white ornamented glass beads, metal beads. Wire wrapped focusing detail, like a first spring leaf, is decorated with aventurine and small glass beads.
The handmade clasp will close on antique bronze chain.

	Lets meet the Spring!

	Lengh – 22 cm
Leaf detail – 5cm x 2.7cm

name: Laurel_pendant
description:
Wrapped into copper, holds a lot of small glass beads, green and as always beautiful aventurine, in the middle of the pendant – long crystal bead with green traces. 
The chain is double, closes with a handmade closure.

	The pendant measures 6cm x 3,2cm + additional pendant upper part, connected to a chain, about 1,5cm.
Chain – 52cm
